# password_whitelist.txt — chat IDs allowed to request passwords from 1Password
#
# Copy this file to password_whitelist.txt and configure it.
# password_whitelist.txt is gitignored and will never be committed.
#
# Only chats listed here can use the password lookup tool.
# The chat must also be in chats_whitelist.txt to be processed at all.
#
# To find your chat IDs run:
#   python tools/list_chats.py
#
# Syntax:
#   one exact chat ID per line
#   inline # comments are supported
#
# Examples:
#
# !abc123:beeper.local             # my personal Telegram DM
# !xyz456:beeper.local             # home server chat
